ass="flex-shrink-0"><div class="p-3 bg-teal-100 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-x h-6 w-6 text-teal-500" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m15 9-6 6"></path><path d="m9 9 6 6"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Seguimientos Perdidos</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Sin indicaciones de acción claras, los pacientes no realizan el seguimiento.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="p-3 bg-teal-100 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-x h-6 w-6 text-teal-500" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m15 9-6 6"></path><path d="m9 9 6 6"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Herramientas Desconectadas</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Usar sistemas separados añade esfuerzo para proveedores y administradores.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="p-3 bg-teal-100 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-x h-6 w-6 text-teal-500" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m15 9-6 6"></path><path d="m9 9 6 6"></path></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Riesgos de Cumplimiento</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Sin notificaciones seguras y conformes, los datos sensibles de pacientes pueden estar expuestos.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-blue-light/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30">Entrega Multicanal</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Alcance a los Pacientes en Su Canal Preferido</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Integrado en Virtual Practice, las notificaciones se entregan automáticamente a través de múltiples canales seguros, sin herramientas adicionales.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4 "><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Notificaciones SMS</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Alertas rápidas y directas a través de su propio gateway de SMS.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4 "><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-mail h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7"></path><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Alertas por Correo Electrónico</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Mensajes claros y detallados con formato enriquecido.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4 "><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0"></path><path d="M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Notificaciones Push Móviles</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Actualizaciones instantáneas a través de la aplicación móvil para pacientes.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4 "><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0"></path><path d="M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Notificaciones Dentro de la Aplicación</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Alertas centralizadas dentro del portal y la aplicación para pacientes.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4 md:col-span-2"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Mensajería de WhatsApp (solo Notificaciones Personalizadas)</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Compatible cuando se integra con su cuenta de WhatsApp Business.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Entrega de notificaciones multicanal en diferentes dispositivos" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_notifications%2Fmultichannel_delivery.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_notifications%2Fmultichannel_delivery.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_notifications%2Fmultichannel_delivery.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Disparadores de notificaciones impulsados por flujos de trabajo" loading="lazy" width="600" height="450" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_notifications%2Fworkflow_driven_triggers.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_notifications%2Fworkflow_driven_triggers.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fpatient_notifications%2Fworkflow_driven_triggers.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-green-success/20 text-green-success px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-green-success/30">Disparadores Impulsados por Flujos de Trabajo</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Comunicación Automatizada para Cada Evento Clave</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Las notificaciones se envían automáticamente, activadas por los eventos que importan en su consultorio.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Notificaciones de Citas</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Confirmaciones, recordatorios y seguimientos</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-green-success flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Alertas de Laboratorio y Documentos</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Avisos de disponibilidad con enlaces de acceso seguro.</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" widt